// Man page for addpass
manAddpass="ADDPASS(1)                       X Shell Manual                       ADDPASS(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    addpass - Add password to rainbow tables
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>addpass</b> [PASSWORD]
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Add custom password to rainbow table database for hash cracking. Performs
    duplicate check before insertion to maintain table integrity. Useful for
    adding commonly used passwords, discovered credentials, and custom
    wordlists to improve cracking success rates.
<b>OPTIONS</b>
    <b>addpass [PASSWORD]</b>
    Add password to rainbow tables
    Checks for duplicates first
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <color=#e4ff34># Add Common Passwords</color>
    <b>addpass password123</b>
    Add weak password

    <b>addpass admin2024</b>
    Add common variant

    <color=#e4ff34># Add Discovered Credentials</color>
    <b>addpass SecureP@ss987</b>
    Add cracked password

    <b>addpass CompanyName123</b>
    Add organization-specific

    <color=#e4ff34># Bulk Addition</color>
    <b>addpass Welcome2024</b>
    Add seasonal password

    <b>addpass Summer2024</b>
    Add another variant
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>rainbow</b>, <b>pass</b>, <b>hc</b>"